# CHANGELOG
<!-- Latest on top -->

## [1.1.0] - 2025-06-06
### Added
- Added Language support for bunker app.

## [1.1.0] - 2025-05-26
### Added
- Added a simple status icon and link to the relay management page in the settings drawer, along with functionality to add, remove, and view detailed status of relays.
- Updated the main screen popup to include a form for editing details such as white and black names, and date input. Added a dropdown to select Site and Round for non-Casual events.

## [1.1.0] - 2025-05-25
### Added
- Added functionality to retrieve and edit user metadata as per NIP-01, including a simple user card in the settings drawer, navigation to a profile edit page, and an edit metadata form for name and picture.

## [1.1.0] - 2025-05-22
- Update splash screen progess bar

## [1.1.0] - 2025-05-21
- Update splash screen

## [1.1.0] - 2025-05-19
### Added
- Added SVG icons for any representation of pieces across the app.

## [1.1.0] - 2025-05-18
### Added
- Added a shady_minions Switch in the settings drawer that will toggle the home default view.

## [1.1.0] - 2025-05-16
### Added
- Added Language support for annotator app.
- Added link to key recovery page on settings drawer
- Added Key recovery options page (show secret key, show mnemonic, delete keys)

## Start of Project (13/05/2025)
